<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV47">
<l>tirikiṉ ṟatuvaṭa mārutan tiṅkaḷven tīmukantu</l>
<l>corikiṉ ṟatatu vumatu kaṇṇaṉviṇ ṇūrtoḻavē</l>
<l>carikiṉ ṟatucaṅkan taṇṇantu ḻāykkuvaṇ ṇampayalai</l>
<l>virikiṉ ṟatumuḻu meyyumeṉ ṉāṅkoleṉ melliyaṟkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Wanders the northern wind. The moon, having drawn up hot fire,</l>
<l>pours [it] forth. That too is that. When worshipping Kaṇṇaṉ’s heavenly town,</l>
<l>[her] conch [bangles] slide down. For [his] cool Tulsi, pallor of</l>
<l>complexion spreads about [her] whole body. What will happen to my soft-natured [girl]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
